#

Tandoori Cauliflower with Spiced Chickpeas

$15.99
350 kcal

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Indian CuisineVegetarian DelightHealthy

Description

A vibrant Tandoori cauliflower served with spiced chickpeas for a hearty vegetarian delight.

Ingredients

  • Cauliflower: 1 medium, cut into florets
  • Greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • Tandoori spice mix: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Chickpeas (canned or cooked): 1 can (15 oz)
  • Cumin powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Coriander powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Fresh cilantro: for garnish
  • Lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
